I am telling you the story 
A state in India name uttrakhand 
There was one king one day he and his wife go to  the temple for their son 
Same any other family also came in that temple for any child 
They say to each other if they get boy and girl they will both each other 
The king got son and other family got daughter 
The king son will died if he not married 
The 5 days little children have to de wedding after their wedding the king died 
Then they not accept wedding 
They both grew up 
They come in each other dreams 
Then they both know that their is something in both of them 
They both said we will wedding each other

The boy come to wedd the girl and  become priest for some time 
The other king knows that he is a king 
Than he gives him poison 
The girl know that she cry a lot 
But with their true love and God the boy alive and fight with the king than they both get wedding and live with each other 
This story is very old story 
I had tell you in short 
The song present the story
